item.title: Animation
item.dc:creator: janahatilova22
item.content:encoded: This project was the first animation project I did in my first year of college. It was fun and I really enjoyed it. I really enjoyed the two characters we had to design for the short animation and the background also. It is very basic and was made using combination of Adobe Illustrator and Adobe Flash.
